\"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies â€” never a grep narrowed to your own files â€” and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {â€¦} â†’ now M: {â€¦}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No râ€¦\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16265,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch â€” Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies â€” Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsiâ€¦ | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn â€” NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use expâ€¦\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16264,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/gate-tool-routing.md\",\n          \"title\": \"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16263,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/finding-is-a-hypothesis.md\",\n          \"title\": \"A Finding Is a Hypothesis Until You Open the Cited Code\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies â€” never ground truth. | Prioritize when: only verdict discipline still holds: never soften an active blocker without new evidence.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15815,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies â€” never a grep narrowed to your own files â€” and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {â€¦} â†’ now M: {â€¦}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No râ€¦\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15814,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch â€” Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies â€” Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsiâ€¦ | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn â€” NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use expâ€¦\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1757,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/010-root-level-review-research-convention\",\n          \"title\": \"...killed-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/010-root-level-review-research-convention/tasks]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"tasks\",\n            \"root\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1751,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/010-root-level-review-research-convention\",\n          \"title\": \"...estration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/010-root-level-review-research-convention/implementation-summary]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"review\",\n            \"root\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8821,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/024-compact-code-graph\",\n          \"title\": \"Deep Research Report: Compact Code Graph â€” Complete Findings [system-spec-kit/024-compact-code-graph/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"code\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8783,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/024-compact-code-graph/030-opencode-graph-plugin\",\n          \"title\": \"Deep Research Report: OpenCode LCM Plugin [system-spec-kit/024-compact-code-graph/030-opencode-graph-plugin/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"code\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8670,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/024-compact-code-graph/019-code-graph-auto-trigger\",\n          \"title\": \"Tasks: Code Graph Auto-Trigger [024/019] [system-spec-kit/024-compact-code-graph/019-code-graph-auto-trigger/tasks]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"tasks\",\n            \"code\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-15T17:33:15.431Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 2031\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781544793395,"end":1781544796728}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0de000b165b40e1b016a30375958308191afded04e120a941a"}},"id":"prt_ecc58352e001kTaWWRrIlaPQ0q","sessionID":"ses_133a82fbbffevAjtqNLJ4lglcd","messageID":"msg_ecc57d5fa001Py08U6IbAjdVxf"}}
